     * @param endY Second point's y-coordinate
     * @param targetX x-coordinate to interpolate
     * @return y-coordinate for `targetX` along the line from (`startX`, `startY`) -> (`endX`, `endY`)
     */
    function linearInterpolation(
        UFixed6 startX,
        Fixed6 startY,
        UFixed6 endX,
        Fixed6 endY,
